gree with that extrapolated from clusters with no break at the\ngroup scale. The analyses of observed velocity dispersion profiles and of the\nFT both suggest that low velocity dispersion groups (compact and loose, X-ray\nemitting or undetected) are quite contaminated by chance projections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jul 2006 13:39:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Jul 2006 22:20:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
