egrees of freedom with a cognitive transmitter or a cognitive\nreceiver.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jul 2006 07:50:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Sep 2006 23:55:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 11 May 2007 20:48:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-07-13"}
